<h2 class="no_toc text-delta" id="table-of-contents">Table of contents</h2>
<hr />
<p>Creating a reusable flow and data makes it easy to manage the solution and apply global changes.</p>

<p><strong>Reusable Flow</strong>: Keep the solution canvas simple by abstracting out repeated actions into a Reusable flow.</p>

<p><strong>Environment Variable</strong>: When the same value gets applied in many actions, use env-variable.</p>
